createBridgeAdapter.t.sol
├── given sender does not have the relevant role
│  └── it should revert with AccessManagedUnauthorized
└── given sender has the relevant role
   ├── given an adapter already exists for the provided bridge ID
   │  └── it should revert with BridgeAdapterAlreadyExists
   └── given an adapter does not already exists for the provided bridge ID
      ├── it should deploy a BridgeAdapter instance for the provided bridge ID
      └── it should emit a BridgeAdapterCreated event
